title: Vegie Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, International, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine
description: Busy restaurant serving a wide range of food and usually large portions. Very typical for Melbourne. Menu includes pizza, stir fry, noodles, roast veggies, pasta, vegan desserts, and more. Open kitchen and extra long communal table seating. Go early for dinner to get a table, otherwise expect to wait.
